{"title":"Terra Emblema machines sub 100g MTB stem w/ 40mm reach for 35mm clamp bars","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/12/terra-emblema-machines-sub-100g-mtb-stem-w-40mm-reach-for-35mm-clamp-bars/","date":1613149078000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span>The new Terra Emblema stem weighs a claimed 99g, making it one of the lightest mountain bike stems on the market. Terra Bikes are a young company operating out of Arezzo, Italy, partnering with the Materia Racing machine shop to produce the Emblema stem. Launching with the 35mm clamp MTB option, Terra have super lightweight gravel bike stems on the way too…</p><h2>Terra Bike Emblema 99g Stem</h2><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian.jpg\" alt=\"terra emblema 99g mtb stem cnc machined aluminium raw finish\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian-1068x801.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian-265x198.jpg 265w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian-1068x801.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-light-weight-stem-italian-265x198.jpg 265w\"></a></p><p>CNC-machined from solid aluminium, the Terra Emblema is a 40mm reach super lightweight stem for 35mm clamp bars. With steel bolts, it weighs a claimed 110g. Swap those out for titanium ones and you knock the weight down to 99.3g.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-bikes-emblema-aluminium-lightweight-stem-mtb.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-bikes-emblema-aluminium-lightweight-stem-mtb.jpg\" alt=\"terra bikes super lightweight 40mm mtb slem 35mm clamp embelma\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-bikes-emblema-aluminium-lightweight-stem-mtb.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-bikes-emblema-aluminium-lightweight-stem-mtb.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-bikes-emblema-aluminium-lightweight-stem-mtb-297x297.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-bikes-emblema-aluminium-lightweight-stem-mtb-800x800.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-bikes-emblema-aluminium-lightweight-stem-mtb-120x120.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-bikes-emblema-aluminium-lightweight-stem-mtb-768x768.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-bikes-emblema-aluminium-lightweight-stem-mtb-696x696.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-bikes-emblema-aluminium-lightweight-stem-mtb-1068x1068.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-bikes-emblema-aluminium-lightweight-stem-mtb-420x420.jpg 420w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-bikes-emblema-aluminium-lightweight-stem-mtb.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-bikes-emblema-aluminium-lightweight-stem-mtb-297x297.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-bikes-emblema-aluminium-lightweight-stem-mtb-800x800.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-bikes-emblema-aluminium-lightweight-stem-mtb-120x120.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-bikes-emblema-aluminium-lightweight-stem-mtb-768x768.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-bikes-emblema-aluminium-lightweight-stem-mtb-696x696.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-bikes-emblema-aluminium-lightweight-stem-mtb-1068x1068.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-bikes-emblema-aluminium-lightweight-stem-mtb-420x420.jpg 420w\"></a></p><p>Terra Bikes say the design focused on placing material at the points of maximum stress, and removing it from areas that experience less stress, allowing them to keep the weight as low as possible. Certified according to ISO 4210-5, the Emblema stem passed all the static lateral and frontal flexion tests it was subjected to.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-machined-lightweight-stem-black.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-machined-lightweight-stem-black.jpg\" alt=\"terra emblema black super lightweight mtb stem 40mm reach 35mm clamp\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-machined-lightweight-stem-black.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-machined-lightweight-stem-black.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-machined-lightweight-stem-black-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-machined-lightweight-stem-black-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-machined-lightweight-stem-black-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-machined-lightweight-stem-black-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-machined-lightweight-stem-black-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-machined-lightweight-stem-black-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-machined-lightweight-stem-black-630x420.jpg 630w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-machined-lightweight-stem-black.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-machined-lightweight-stem-black-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-machined-lightweight-stem-black-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-machined-lightweight-stem-black-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-machined-lightweight-stem-black-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-machined-lightweight-stem-black-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-machined-lightweight-stem-black-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-machined-lightweight-stem-black-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>45mm and 35mm reach options are on the way for 35mm clamp bars. Terra Bikes are also developing a 31.8mm clamp version for gravel with 60mm and 65mm reach options.</p><h3>Pricing &amp; Availability</h3><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/terra-emblema-super-lightweight-mtb-stems-all-colors.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.co